description.narrative:
Higher education institutions in Sudan and Ethiopia, and through international partnerships, institutions in the EU/UK; 
University students (mostly undergraduates), particularly women;
University researchers, particularly women;
National and local government Ministries and other authorities through their connections with higher education institutions and peacebuilding;
Civil society and non-governmental organisations engaged in peacebuilding activities;
National and regional networks and organisations in peacebuilding.
